## The Verdict

Dreamdata earns its 4.7/5 G2 rating. The journey visualization is genuinely best-in-class, the support is exceptional, and the attribution capabilities are solid for mid-market B2B.

**Choose Dreamdata if** you're a mid-market B2B team with $750+/mo budget, you value visual journey mapping, and you can invest 1-3 months in setup and learning.

**Look elsewhere if** you need quick time-to-value, custom dashboards, or you're budget-constrained. [Dreamdata alternatives](/articles/dreamdata-alternatives) covers 6 options across different price points and use cases.

